                  <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe </roleName> <persName ref="PRS9152TaklaHa">Takla Hāymānot I</persName> shocked by the patricide. 
                  However, in the same year <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe </roleName> <persName ref="PRS9152TaklaHa">Takla Hāymānot I </persName> was 
                  killed and then he continued to serve as chronicler in the court for a short time. However, he resumed officially his pen as a hitoriographer during the reign
                  of  <roleName type="title">ʾaṣe </roleName><persName ref="PRS2377Bakaffa">Bakāffā</persName>.  </floruit>
